title: Panasonic 1.5 Ton 3 Star Hot and Cold Wi-Fi Inverter Smart Split AC (Copper, 7 in 1 Convertible with AI, Twin Cool, PM 0.1 Filter, CS/CU-KZ18ZKYF, 2023 Model, White)
product_description: Beat the heat with Panasonic 1.5 Ton 3 Star Hot & Cold Inverter Wi-Fi enabled Split Smart AC. Equipped with a split inverter, it is highly energy efficient. Its twin rotary speed compressor consumes minimum energy making it cost-effective and environment friendly. The advanced Hot and Cold feature ensures to keep you cool during summer and warm during winter. With 7 in 1 convertible modes and an additional AI mode, it can smartly detect the room temperature, forecast the right cooling capacity and change fan speed to provide optimal cooling via inbuilt sensors and artificial intelligence. Aside from energy saving, PM 0.1 filter ensures healthy cooling by removing PM 0.1 dust particles in air. Integration of this smart AC with AI enabled MirAie app adds to the overall convenience via seamless hands free operation through voice control and ability to set customised sleep cycles. It is engineered with a wide voltage range reducing the damages from voltage fluctuations. The Shield Blu+ creates an anti-corrosive layer on indoor and outdoor units to prevent scratches and leakage.
